# BBQ Chicken Flatbread Pizza

> A mouthwatering fusion of smoky BBQ sauce, tender chicken, gooey cheese, and crispy flatbread that will take your taste buds on a delicious adventure! #chicken

![](C37C337B-450F-4B48-AA75-2261CF023853.jpg)

Preheat your oven to 550 degrees.

- Naan | 2 | 
- Butter | Salted, 4 tbsp | 
- Garlic | 1 clove | Minced

Soften and mix the butter and garlic and apply as a thin layer on top of the flatbread.

- Colby Cheese |  | Shredded
- Chicken | 1/2 cup | grilled cut into bite-size pieces

Sprinkle with cheese and top with grilled chicken.

- BBQ Sauce | Sweet Baby Rays | 
- French Fried Onions | 2 tbsp | 

Drizzle BBQ sauce on top and sprinkle with french fried onions.

Bake for 7-10 minutes (until cheese is melted).

- Green Onion | 2 | Sliced

Remove from oven, sprinkle with green onions and serve.
